 <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/bfirionavie.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=dalninil>Dalninil</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 162<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(2/2/02 10:42:44 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm4.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=317.topic&index=7>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   hmmm.....</span><hr size=1> Ok, this server is a comunity, but unlike real life there is no special passes. Or known areas, or any of the other things that can set a community within a community apart. The only thing you have is (roleplay preferred) so anyone that feels like picking up the box and giving it a whirl is instantly in your bar doing who knows what. Perhaps they are trying to roleplay or perhaps they are just learning the game, or perhaps being cleric007 just upset them and they are here to ensure that they are cleric001 or 002, everyone that restarted on this server did it for a reason and everyones reason is different. So unless you're planning on making up some backstage FV passes, just deal with the fact that there are going to be a mix of folks in your bar. Some family and some not, you can't protect your self with your walls against some 14 year old that just wants to watch the pretty numbers, who is behind the screne. Personally I like to roleplay hence I'm here but guess what if Joe003 doesn't want to I'm not going to throw a fit about it. I'll not deal with him and ice hit out of every group i'm in until he feels he wishs to roleplay just a bit. I don't judge folks out of the blue, and don't get upset because there are greifers out there folks that just like to spin folks up in RL. This is a game have fun with it. This is not a family matter or even close to one.<br>
